@* CEBU FOOD STORIES *@
<section class="section">
    <div class="section-header" data-aos="fade-up">
        <h2>📖 Cebu Food Stories</h2>
        <p>Stories from our vibrant food culture</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card-grid">
        <div class="story-card" data-aos="fade-up">
            <div class="card-image">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1569694119452-2b7eae2e4cbc?w=600&h=400&fit=crop" alt="Lechon History">
            </div>
            <div class="card-content">
                <h3>Why Cebu Lechon is the Best in the World</h3>
                <p class="card-location">By Maria Santos · 5 min read</p>
                <p>The secrets behind Cebu's most iconic dish, from family recipes to modern interpretations.</p>
                <a href="#" class="read-more">Read Story →</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="story-card" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
            <div class="card-image">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1537047902294-62a40c20a6ae?w=600&h=400&fit=crop" alt="Sutukil Story">
            </div>
            <div class="card-content">
                <h3>The Story Behind Sutukil</h3>
                <p class="card-location">By Chef Miguel · 4 min read</p>
                <p>How Sugba, Tula, Kilaw became the heart of Cebu's seafood culture.</p>
                <a href="#" class="read-more">Read Story →</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="story-card" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
            <div class="card-image">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1442512595331-e89e73853f31?w=600&h=400&fit=crop" alt="Hidden Cafes">
            </div>
            <div class="card-content">
                <h3>Hidden Cafes in IT Park You Need to Try</h3>
                <p class="card-location">By Alex Reyes · 6 min read</p>
                <p>From secret rooftops to underground coffee spots.</p>
                <a href="#" class="read-more">Read Story →</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .btn-tried {
        background: none;
        border: 1px solid var(--burnt-orange);
        color: var(--burnt-orange);
        padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
        border-radius: 30px;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        cursor: pointer;
        margin-top: 0.8rem;
        transition: var(--transition);
        width: 100%;
    }

        .btn-tried:hover {
            background: var(--burnt-orange);
            color: white;
        }

    .progress-bar {
        background: var(--bg-elevated);
        border-radius: 10px;
        height: 6px;
        margin: 0.8rem 0 0.5rem;
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    .progress {
        background: var(--gradient-warm);
        height: 100%;
        border-radius: 10px;
    }

    .seats-left {
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        color: var(--text-secondary);
    }

    .read-more {
        color: var(--burnt-orange);
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        display: inline-block;
        margin-top: 0.8rem;
    }

        .read-more:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
</style>